Package: apmrt
Type: Package
Title: Makes my life easier
Version: 0.1.9
Author: Alexandre Torrejano
Maintainer: The package maintainer <alexandretorrejano@gmail.com>
Description: Contains some functions that encompass code chunks that I've had to repeat on a daily basis.
    Notably: 
    -a file reader and a file writer that wrap different functions from data.table, openxlsx and readxl;
    -a function the wipes the environment of all temporary data;
    -a function that sets frequent options and loads frequent packages while setting the working dir to source file location.
